{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1575b01a89","title":"毛泽东在转发邓子恢关于老根据地干部情况报告时加写的话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"05db4ebc36","index":0,"year":1954,"month":1,"day":4,"articleId":"1575b01a89"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e80e0393f3","type":"title","text":"毛泽东在转发邓子恢关于老根据地干部情况报告时加写的话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1575b01a89"},{"id":"1e7411af64","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1575b01a89"},{"id":"1e91395f88","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1575b01a89"},{"id":"02555112e9","type":"paragraph","text":"此外，不但老根据地应这样做，一切晚解放区也应大体上这样做，也应用极大的注意力培养和提拔地方干部。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1575b01a89"},{"id":"b2bd25fea4","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1575b01a89"},{"id":"d2d0569f2d","type":"paragraph","text":"所谓干部地方化，当然不是说地方高级和中级领导机关都要用本地人，不能用外地人，相反是必须用必要的外地人的，现在如此，将来还会如此。在农业机械化实施的时候，农村技术人员也是要用一些外地人的。我在这里说的主要是指目前县区干部的情况。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1575b01a89"}],"page":{"id":"cd17e46d59","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1575b01a89","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}